snippet.textDisplay: Well done u guys for reaching out to all kinds of communities in Pakistan.. I'm from the UK and see soo many things being done for deaf, diabled, blind and these communities but never have seen anything done in Pakistan.. well done for branching out Coke Studio and introducing us people (who can hear) to the life of someone who can't.. seeing them enjoying music which is a basic thing in my life, bought alot of joy to me and some tears too.. Thank you for making me appreciate my ability to hear and for showing me the joy that music bought to the deaf community.. Alhamdulillah.. Keep it up.. Luv from London UK xxx
